 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Firewall Engineer Capgemini 8,227 reviews Atlanta, GA 30328 Capgemini 8,227 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Contract Full Job Description Duration :12+Months 
Responsibilities : 
The Palo Alto firewall engineer in the EMEA in region will be leading and performing the planning, setup, and migrations of legacy firewall platforms to Palo Alto Next Generation Firewalls.
 Once the legacy code is migrated, the firewall engineer will use Palo Alto expedition to analyze the legacy firewall code and develop detailed recommendations and implementation plans for APP-ID Adoption, Rule Enrichment, and Machine Learning rule replacement and consolidation.
 Finally, the engineer will lead the code enhancements as recommended. The resource will report on status, identify risk, and give updates to the Regional Lead. 
Requirements : 
Certified Palo Alto firewall professional with extensive experience migrating multiple vendor platforms to Palo Alto NGFWs using Expedition and Panorama.
 In addition to the migration of complex legacy firewall code, the engineer must also have proven experience analyzing migrated firewall code and developing written recommendations and implementation plans for APP-ID Adoption, Rule Enrichment, and Machine Learning rule replacement and consolidation. 
